snippet: A passer-by reported the men, believed in their 20s, sitting with bloodstained white T-shirts in a legally parked car on West 122nd Street.
abstract: Three men are found dead inside a BMW sedan near the campus of Columbia University following an apparent shooting; identities of the victims are not released.
